org.hibernate.ogm.options.navigation.source.impl

Interface OptionValueSource

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnnotationOptionValueSource, ConfigurationOptionValueSource, ProgrammaticOptionValueSource

    public interface OptionValueSource
    A source for option values. Implementations retrieve option values e.g. using annotations, API invocations or configuration values.
    Author:
    Gunnar Morling

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      OptionsContainer getEntityOptions(Class<?> entityType)
      Returns an OptionsContainer with the entity-level options of the given type.
      OptionsContainer getGlobalOptions()
      Returns an OptionsContainer with global-level options.
      OptionsContainer getPropertyOptions(Class<?> entityType, String propertyName)
      Returns an OptionsContainer with the property-level options of the given property.

    • Method Detail

      • getGlobalOptions

        OptionsContainer getGlobalOptions()
        Returns an OptionsContainer with global-level options.
        Returns:

      • getEntityOptions

        OptionsContainer getEntityOptions(Class<?> entityType)
        Returns an OptionsContainer with the entity-level options of the given type.
        Parameters:
        entityType - the type to retrieve the options from
        Returns:

      • getPropertyOptions

        OptionsContainer getPropertyOptions(Class<?> entityType,
                                    String propertyName)
        Returns an OptionsContainer with the property-level options of the given property.
        Parameters:
        entityType - type declaring the property to retrieve the options from
        propertyName - name of the property to retrieve the options from
        Returns:
        an option container with options of the given property; may be empty but never null
